    "title": "Buffalo’s Breakthrough: The Sabres’ Relentless Climb to the Top",
    "tag": "",
    "content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"2\" id=\"p-rc_6442862ed1ba96fb-21\"><span data-path-to-node=\"2,0\">The Buffalo Sabres have redefined the term \"dominance\" over the past week. Once a frequent target of league-wide criticism for their long playoff drought, the organization has been transformed under Lindy Ruff into a legitimate offensive powerhouse. As of March 10, 2026, the Sabres held the NHL's longest active winning streak at eight games—a feat notable for the fact that every single victory was secured in regulation time.</span><span data-path-to-node=\"2,1\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><source-footnote _nghost-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></span><span data-path-to-node=\"2,2\"> This level of consistent, decisive play hasn't been seen from the franchise in 20 years.<br><br></span><span data-path-to-node=\"2,3\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><source-footnote _nghost-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"3\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c2756209179=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c2756209179=\"\" _nghost-ng-c36415296=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c36415296=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p><p data-path-to-node=\"3\" id=\"p-rc_6442862ed1ba96fb-22\"><span data-path-to-node=\"3,0\">The turning point for this roster came on December 9, 2025. Since that date, Buffalo hasn't just been good; they’ve been the gold standard of the NHL. They lead the league in nearly every critical statistical category over the last three months, including points percentage, regulation wins, and goals per game.</span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,1\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><source-footnote _nghost-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,2\"> This is no fluke; it's the result of a revamped defensive structure and the explosive development of their young core.<br><br></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c2756209179=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c2756209179=\"\" _nghost-ng-c36415296=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c36415296=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p><p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">League Rankings (Since Dec. 9, 2025):</b></p><ul data-path-to-node=\"5\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" id=\"p-rc_6442862ed1ba96fb-23\"><span data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Points Percentage (PTS%):</b> 0.833 (1st in NHL) </span><span data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0,1\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><source-footnote _nghost-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2874455147=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c2756209179=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c2756209179=\"\" _nghost-ng-c36415296=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c36415296=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" id=\"p-rc_6442862ed1ba96fb-24\"><span data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Regulation Wins:</b> 26 (1st in NHL) </span><span data-path-to-node